REQUIRED LIBRARIES
================================================================================

 + OpenGL
 + The OpenGL utility toolkit
 + The OpenGL utility library


Installation on Ubuntu:

> apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev


COMPILATION / INSTALLATION
================================================================================

Edit config.mk and call 

> make clean install


CONTROLS
================================================================================

 drag'n'drop  Rotate pointcloud
 mousewheel   Zoom
 i,o,p        Increase, reset, decrease Pointsize
 a,d          Move left, right
 w,s          Move forward, backward
 q,e          Move up, down
 f            Flip pointcloud
 y,x          Invert rotation
 +,-          Zoom in, out
 <esc>        Quit
